<br>
1)  Vendors in DF were selling items for gold, not for seals.  Too bad I took the wife out for lunch today, or I'd have full diamond gear for everyone.  Including the newbies.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I think Mythic is definitely going to have to do a character rollback.<br>
<br>
2)  Group Purge destroys all the pets in the group.  While we aren't Hibs so we don't get it in the first place ... I found this one incredibly funny.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START >: --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/mad.gif ALT=">:"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )<br>
<br>
3)  Don't use the backup styles until there's some confirmation that they have fixed the problem -- it drains the stamina for both the style and the backup.  Oh .. and at least for assassins, it doesn't work anyway -- at least as of this morning.  (I don't know about the melee classes using the main weapon lines)<br>
<br>
Along with that -- apparently if you are a melee type trying to chase someone down and whack them with a style ... it's going to be rougher with your styles constantly canceled as they run out of range.  Lots of griping about that at the moment.<br>
<br>
4)  Mobs are apparently regenning health at an insane rate.  I thought Curio and I were having a bad run of luck this morning, but apparently soloers are kinda screwed at the moment.<br>
<br>
5)  Be sure to check the boards before you buy something with those realm point rewards -- apparently a lot of them are extremely broken at the moment.  (Besides the all too funny petkiller)<br>
<br>
6)  There's some other exploit running rampant with salvage, apparently something to do with mithril ... but I don't know the details.  <br>
<br>
Great job Mythic!  Way to go!  <br>
<br>
Even if I can't play right now, it's just too funny to hear about what's going on .. they really should have gotten the automated character copies going so people could test on Pendragon.<br>
<br>
